  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Identify the physical conditions of static equilibrium.</item>
<item>Draw a free-body diagram for a rigid body acted on by forces.</item>
<item>Explain how the conditions for equilibrium allow us to solve statics problems.</item>
</list></md:abstract>
